></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>命中修正\n</th>\n<td>+0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>武器技能类别\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>规格\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"双手 (page does not exist)\">双手</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>5 <a href=\"/wiki/Zm/zh-CN\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Zm/zh-CN\">zm</a><br />（+10/正数附魔等级）\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">80</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>材料\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<dl><dd><i>“长勾刀”、“修枝刀”重定向至此。</i></dd></dl>\n<p><b>割草铁</b>（guisarme）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"武器\">武器</a>。它是一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>，由<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>制成，未<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鉴定 (page does not exist)\">鉴定</a>时外观为<b>修枝钩</b>（pruning hook）。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">起源</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#NetHack_Fourk\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">NetHack Fourk</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#xNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">xNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#EvilHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">EvilHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%AD%A6%E5%8D%AB%E5%91%98&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"警卫员 (page does not exist)\">警卫员</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"士兵 (page does not exist)\">士兵</a>在生成时有可能<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"怪物起始物品 (page does not exist)\">携带</a>割草铁<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>割草铁对<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"小型 (page does not exist)\">小型</a>怪物的伤害在长柄武器中是不错的水平，重量也比较轻，但是对大型怪物的伤害较低。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>割草铁最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_1.3d\" title=\"NetHack 1.3d\">NetHack 1.3d</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"起源\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\">起源</span></h2>\n<div class=\"noprint sidebox\">\n<div style=\"float: left;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"维基百科\"><img alt=\"维基百科\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png/50px-Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 60px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:Main_Page\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:Main Page\">维基百科</a>相关条目：\n<div style=\"margin-left: 10px;\"><i><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Search/Guisarme\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Special:Search/Guisarme\">Guisarme </a></b></i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:150px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Guisarmes.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/5/52/Guisarmes.png\" width=\"148\" height=\"155\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Guisarmes.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>割草铁</div></div></div>\n<p>割草铁（guisarme，也可拼作gisarme、giserne或bisarme）是11至15世纪期间在欧洲出现的一种长柄武器，可能起源自日耳曼民族——和多数长柄武器一样，此类武器最初的形式很难通过史料还原，对现存武器的鉴别也容易产生不准确的结果。多数标注是割草铁的图片里面的武器事实上是<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%96%A9%E7%9F%9B\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"斩矛\">斩矛</a>叉，是一种在刀背上加装矛头的斩矛。\n</p><p>现代关于割草铁的形制演变和应用有两种主流说法。一种说法是，割草铁是农民们将修枝钩镰与长柄结合起来的产物。早期的割草铁通常只有一个固定在长柄一端的钩状刃，后来发展出刀背上加装小型倒钩的设计——再后来，武器工匠们将割草铁的倒钩与不同长柄武器的设计结合起来，由此诞生的武器基本都在名称里带有“草铁”的词缀，例如“<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8D%89%E9%93%81%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E9%94%B2\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"草铁长柄锲\">草铁长柄锲</a>”（bill-guisarme）、“草铁宽刃刀”（voulge-guisarme）和“草铁剑刃戟”（glaive-guisarme），等等。另一种说法则认为割草铁是一种有弦月形斧刃的长柄斧，该说法源自英文诗歌《高文爵士与绿衣骑士》（<i>Sir Gawain and the Green Knight</i>），此诗中使用“giserne”和“axe”两个词称呼同一种武器。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Guisarme/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"NetHack_Fourk\">NetHack Fourk</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_Fourk\" title=\"NetHack Fourk\">NetHack Fourk</a> removes the guisarme and many other polearms.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"xNetHack\">xNetHack</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/XNetHack\" title=\"XNetHack\">xNetHack</a> removes the guisarme and many other polearms.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a>, a guisarme can be created at a <a href=\"/wiki/Forge_(dungeon_feature)\" title=\"Forge (dungeon feature)\">forge</a> by combining a <a href=\"/wiki/Grappling_hook\" title=\"Grappling hook\">grappling hook</a> and a <a href=\"/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\">spear</a>; a guisarme can be combined with a spear to create a bill-guisarme. This also applies to <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>请参阅<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器的百科文本</a>。</i></dd></dl>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L194\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 194</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926183928\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.035 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.049 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 418/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2543/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4586/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 685/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 448/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   32.117      1 -total\n 26.64%    8.557      1 Template:Refsrc\n 19.92%    6.398      1 Template:Languages\n 14.35%    4.609      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 13.66%    4.387      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 12.12%    3.894      1 Template:Weapon/zh-CN\n 10.08%    3.238      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n  7.37%    2.367      1 Template:Wikipedia/zh-CN\n  6.15%    1.975      1 Template:Top_icon\n  5.96%    1.914      1 Template:Refsrc/link\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wi